  "id": "019cdcdc-fd01-7d11-b0d7-99b2110d05dc",
  "content": "### New REST endpoints\n### New MCP tools\n\n### Bug fix: Route existing search through pipeline\n\n`POST /v1/memories/search` and `corvia_search` MCP tool are updated to route through `VectorRetriever` instead of raw `store.search()`. Same API contract, now with proper RBAC and visibility filtering.\n\n\n### AppState update\n\n```rust\npub struct AppState {\n    pub store: Arc<dyn QueryableStore>,\n    pub engine: Arc<dyn InferenceEngine>,\n    pub coordinator: Option<Arc<AgentCoordinator>>,\n    pub rag: Arc<RagPipeline>,\n}\n```\n",
